{"tid":2114602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國據報尋求日本協助建5G　NEC富士通或成供應商","createTime":"2020-07-19T03:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T04:33:03.000Z","uid":57376,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c83d25e667103af7fd009abafe9bb9c329af4910","tid":2114602,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:18:17.000Z","msg":"《日經新聞》報道，英國政府已經向日本尋求協助，參與建設5G網絡。英國上星期宣布禁用華為建設5G，報道表示，英國官員星期四曾經與日本官員在東京會面，英國可能會以日本的NEC與富士通，作為替代供應商。消息指，英國政府正努力引入新的設備供應商，維持在5G建設上的競爭力。英國駐日本大使館、日本內閣官方長官辦公室，以及NEC與富士通都未有就事件回應。<br />\n<br />\n2020-07-19 11:12:22<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54362cd0b6de69688b9d61af2e7328ff59b4df42","tid":2114602,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:18:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a63f05d46b7f8faba463c29d9255db97b8c0b78a","tid":2114602,"uid":36152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:21:35.000Z","msg":"Fujitsu, Shaping tomorrow with you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b97c4ef9fbbd847cf59e75eede07de23ad62be","tid":2114602,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:23:48.000Z","msg":"大英同大日本合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4cdeaeac786036c3c01c6ed48e5552c9f89243","tid":2114602,"uid":88743,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:25:42.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n成日打飛機華為掌握5G高科技<br />\n原來間間公司都識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己賤價想霸市佔率就唔好講到自己點勁點勁啦<br />\n又串鳩英國唔用華為要付出代價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\non9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},